query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('area',
'banach-spaces',
'brownian-motion',
'eigenvalues-eigenvectors',
'extension-field',
'functional-equations',
'graph-theory',
'group-theory',
'grub2',
'indefinite-integrals',
'linear-algebra',
'model-theory',
'normed-spaces',
'polynomials',
'virtualbox')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math') group by t1.name;
